Pre-Game Insights: Deschamps decided against risking Mbappe for the contest with the Netherlands due to his recent injury.
Deschamps is expected to have Mbappe available for France's final group game against Poland on June 25, which will be played at the Westfalenstadion.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Paderborn players were told to go easy on Mbappe to let him enjoy a simple re-integration into the team.
Mbappe scored twice and laid on two assists in a training match against Paderborn's Under-21s.
